                             18:package org.apache.poi.hslf.dev;                                                                                                                                                 
                             19:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             20:import java.io.IOException;                                                                                                                                                      
                             21:import java.io.PrintStream;                                                                                                                                                      
                             22:import java.util.Locale;                                                                                                                                                         
                             23:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             24:import org.apache.commons.io.output.UnsynchronizedByteArrayOutputStream;                                                                                                         
                             25:import org.apache.poi.ddf.DefaultEscherRecordFactory;                                                                                                                            
                             26:import org.apache.poi.ddf.EscherContainerRecord;                                                                                                                                 
                             27:import org.apache.poi.ddf.EscherRecord;                                                                                                                                          
                             28:import org.apache.poi.ddf.EscherTextboxRecord;                                                                                                                                   
                             29:import org.apache.poi.hslf.record.EscherTextboxWrapper;                                                                                                                          
                             30:import org.apache.poi.hslf.record.HSLFEscherRecordFactory;                                                                                                                       
                             31:import org.apache.poi.hslf.record.Record;                                                                                                                                        
                             32:import org.apache.poi.hslf.record.StyleTextPropAtom;                                                                                                                             
                             33:import org.apache.poi.hslf.record.TextBytesAtom;                                                                                                                                 
                             34:import org.apache.poi.hslf.record.TextCharsAtom;                                                                                                                                 
                             35:import org.apache.poi.hslf.usermodel.HSLFSlideShowImpl;                                                                                                                          
                             36:import org.apache.poi.util.HexDump;                                                                                                                                              
                             37:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             38:/**                                                                                                                                                                              
                             39: * This class provides a way to view the contents of a powerpoint file.                                                                                                          
                             40: * It will use the record layer to grok the contents of the file, and                                                                                                            
                             41: *  will print out what it finds.                                                                                                                                                
                             42: */                                                                                                                                                                              
                             43:public final class SlideShowRecordDumper {                                                                                                                                       
                             44:    static final String tabs = "\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t";                                                                                                           
                             45:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             46:    private final boolean optVerbose;                                                                                                                                            
                             47:    private final boolean optEscher;                                                                                                                                             
                             48:    private final HSLFSlideShowImpl doc;                                                                                                                                         
                             49:    private final PrintStream ps;                                                                                                                                                
                             50:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             51:    /**                                                                                                                                                                          
                             52:     * right now this function takes one parameter: a ppt file, and outputs a                                                                                                    
                             53:     * dump of what it contains                                                                                                                                                  
                             54:     */                                                                                                                                                                          
                             55:    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {                                                                                                                  
                             56:        boolean verbose = false;                                                                                                                                                 
                             57:        boolean escher = false;                                                                                                                                                  
                             58:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             59:        int ndx = 0;                                                                                                                                                             
                             60:        for (; ndx < args.length; ndx++) {                                                                                                                                       
                             61:            if (args[ndx].charAt(0) != '-')                                                                                                                                      
                             62:                break;                                                                                                                                                           
                             63:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             64:            if (args[ndx].equals("-escher")) {                                                                                                                                   
                             65:                escher = true;                                                                                                                                                   
                             66:            } else if (args[ndx].equals("-verbose")) {                                                                                                                           
                             67:                verbose = true;                                                                                                                                                  
                             68:            } else {                                                                                                                                                             
                             69:                printUsage();                                                                                                                                                    
                             70:                return;                                                                                                                                                          
                             71:            }                                                                                                                                                                    
                             72:        }                                                                                                                                                                        
                             73:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             74:        // parsed any options, expect exactly one remaining arg (filename)                                                                                                       
                             75:        if (ndx != args.length - 1) {                                                                                                                                            
                             76:            printUsage();                                                                                                                                                        
                             77:            return;                                                                                                                                                              
                             78:        }                                                                                                                                                                        
                             79:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             80:        String filename = args[ndx];                                                                                                                                             
                             81:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             82:        SlideShowRecordDumper foo = new SlideShowRecordDumper(System.out, filename, verbose, escher);                                                                            
                             83:        try {                                                                                                                                                                    
                             84:            foo.printDump();                                                                                                                                                     
                             85:        } finally {                                                                                                                                                              
                             86:            foo.doc.close();                                                                                                                                                     
                             87:        }                                                                                                                                                                        
                             88:    }                                                                                                                                                                            
                             89:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             90:    public static void printUsage() {                                                                                                                                            
                             91:        System.err.println("Usage: SlideShowRecordDumper [-escher] [-verbose] <filename>");                                                                                      
                             92:        System.err.println("Valid Options:");                                                                                                                                    
                             93:        System.err.println("-escher\t\t: dump contents of escher records");                                                                                                      
                             94:        System.err.println("-verbose\t: dump binary contents of each record");                                                                                                   
                             95:    }                                                                                                                                                                            
                             96:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             97:    /**                                                                                                                                                                          
                             98:     * Constructs a Powerpoint dump from fileName. Parses the document                                                                                                           
                             99:     * and dumps out the contents                                                                                                                                                
                             100:     *                                                                                                                                                                          
                             101:     * @param fileName The name of the file to read.                                                                                                                            
                             102:     * @throws IOException if there is a problem while parsing the document.                                                                                                    
                             103:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             104:    public SlideShowRecordDumper(PrintStream ps, String fileName, boolean verbose, boolean escher)                                                                              
                             105:    throws IOException {                                                                                                                                                        
                             106:        this.ps = ps;                                                                                                                                                           
                             107:        optVerbose = verbose;                                                                                                                                                   
                             108:        optEscher = escher;                                                                                                                                                     
                             109:        doc = new HSLFSlideShowImpl(fileName);                                                                                                                                  
                             110:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             111:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             112:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             113:    public void printDump() throws IOException {                                                                                                                                
                             114:        // Prints out the records in the tree                                                                                                                                   
                             115:        walkTree(0, 0, doc.getRecords(), 0);                                                                                                                                    
                             116:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             117:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             118:    public String makeHex(int number, int padding) {                                                                                                                            
                             119:        StringBuilder hex = new StringBuilder(Integer.toHexString(number).toUpperCase(Locale.ROOT));                                                                            
                             120:        while (hex.length() < padding) {                                                                                                                                        
                             121:            hex.insert(0, "0");                                                                                                                                                 
                             122:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             123:        return hex.toString();                                                                                                                                                  
                             124:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             125:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             126:    public String reverseHex(String s) {                                                                                                                                        
                             127:        StringBuilder ret = new StringBuilder();                                                                                                                                
                             128:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             129:        // Get to a multiple of two                                                                                                                                             
                             130:        int pos = 0;                                                                                                                                                            
                             131:        if ((s.length() & 1) == 1) {                                                                                                                                            
                             132:            ret.append(0);                                                                                                                                                      
                             133:            pos++;                                                                                                                                                              
                             134:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             135:        for (char c : s.toCharArray()) {                                                                                                                                        
                             136:            if (pos > 0 && (pos & 1) == 0) {                                                                                                                                    
                             137:                ret.append(' ');                                                                                                                                                
                             138:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             139:            ret.append(c);                                                                                                                                                      
                             140:            pos++;                                                                                                                                                              
                             141:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             142:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             143:        return ret.toString();                                                                                                                                                  
                             144:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             145:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             146:    public int getDiskLen(org.apache.poi.hslf.record.Record r) throws IOException {                                                                                             
                             147:        int diskLen = 0;                                                                                                                                                        
                             148:        if (r != null) {                                                                                                                                                        
                             149:            UnsynchronizedByteArrayOutputStream baos = UnsynchronizedByteArrayOutputStream.builder().get();                                                                     
                             150:            r.writeOut(baos);                                                                                                                                                   
                             151:            diskLen = baos.size();                                                                                                                                              
                             152:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             153:        return diskLen;                                                                                                                                                         
                             154:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             155:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             156:    public String getPrintableRecordContents(org.apache.poi.hslf.record.Record r) throws IOException {                                                                          
                             157:        if (r == null) {                                                                                                                                                        
                             158:            return "<<null>>";                                                                                                                                                  
                             159:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             160:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             161:        UnsynchronizedByteArrayOutputStream baos = UnsynchronizedByteArrayOutputStream.builder().get();                                                                         
                             162:        r.writeOut(baos);                                                                                                                                                       
                             163:        byte[] b = baos.toByteArray();                                                                                                                                          
                             164:        return HexDump.dump(b, 0, 0);                                                                                                                                           
                             165:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             166:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             167:    public void printEscherRecord(EscherRecord er, int indent) {                                                                                                                
                             168:        if (er instanceof EscherContainerRecord) {                                                                                                                              
                             169:            printEscherContainerRecord( (EscherContainerRecord)er, indent );                                                                                                    
                             170:        } else if (er instanceof EscherTextboxRecord) {                                                                                                                         
                             171:            printEscherTextBox( (EscherTextboxRecord)er, indent );                                                                                                              
                             172:        } else {                                                                                                                                                                
                             173:            ps.print( tabs.substring(0, indent) );                                                                                                                              
                             174:            ps.println(er);                                                                                                                                                     
                             175:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             176:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             177:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             178:    private void printEscherTextBox( EscherTextboxRecord tbRecord, int indent ) {                                                                                               
                             179:        String ind = tabs.substring(0, indent);                                                                                                                                 
                             180:        ps.println(ind+"EscherTextboxRecord:");                                                                                                                                 
                             181:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             182:        EscherTextboxWrapper etw = new EscherTextboxWrapper(tbRecord);                                                                                                          
                             183:        Record prevChild = null;                                                                                                                                                
                             184:        for (Record child : etw.getChildRecords()) {                                                                                                                            
                             185:            if (child instanceof StyleTextPropAtom) {                                                                                                                           
                             186:                // need preceding Text[Chars|Bytes]Atom to initialize the data structure                                                                                        
                             187:                String text;                                                                                                                                                    
                             188:                if (prevChild instanceof TextCharsAtom) {                                                                                                                       
                             189:                    text = ((TextCharsAtom)prevChild).getText();                                                                                                                
                             190:                } else if (prevChild instanceof TextBytesAtom) {                                                                                                                
                             191:                    text = ((TextBytesAtom)prevChild).getText();                                                                                                                
                             192:                } else {                                                                                                                                                        
                             193:                    ps.println(ind+"Error! Couldn't find preceding TextAtom for style");                                                                                        
                             194:                    continue;                                                                                                                                                   
                             195:                }                                                                                                                                                               
                             196:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             197:                StyleTextPropAtom tsp = (StyleTextPropAtom)child;                                                                                                               
                             198:                tsp.setParentTextSize(text.length());                                                                                                                           
                             199:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             200:            ps.println(ind+ child);                                                                                                                                             
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             </code>                                                                                                                                                                             
                             <code>                                                                                                                                                                              
                             poi-scratchpad/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/hslf/dev/SlideShowDumper.java:1-200                                                                                                     
                             ```
